toys.name: LEGO City Fire Rescue Boat 60373
toys.description: Exciting firefighting adventures await with this LEGO City Fire Rescue Boat (60373) playset, featuring a cool toy fireboat and speedboat dinghy. Kids can launch LEGO water elements from the boat’s extinguisher and firefighter jetpack to knock out the LEGO flames. Just add the 3 included minifigures and let the fun begin. Digital building fun for kids aged 5+

toys.name: LEGO City Police Car and Muscle Car Chase 60415
toys.description: Unleash high-speed fun and excitement with this police car toy playset for kids aged 6 and over. The LEGO City Police Car and Muscle Car Chase (60415) set for boys and girls features a cool police interceptor and a getaway vehicle, plus officer and crook minifigures for fun role play and storytelling.

toys.name: LEGO Technic Dump Truck 42147
toys.description: Looking for a treat for building site fans? Kids aged 7 and over will love building and playing with this LEGO Technic Dump Truck (42147) toy set. It’s a great introduction to the world of LEGO Technic and helps young builders learn new engineering skills.

toys.name: LEGO Technic NEOM McLaren Extreme E Race Car 42166
toys.description: ooking for an exciting gift for kids who love racing car toys? This pull-back car for boys and girls aged 7+ delivers thrills at every turn. First youngsters can enjoy building the LEGO® Technic NEOM McLaren Extreme E Race Car (42166).

toys.name: Barbie Self-Care Rise & Relax Doll
toys.description: Kids can practice mindfulness and meditate with the Barbie Rise and Relax doll to help feel relaxed during the day and to fall asleep at night! This fully posable doll has 6 different guided meditations with light, sound and soothing music across 2 different modes: Daytime and Night.

toys.name: Barbie Doll and Pool Playset
toys.description: Slide into summer fun with Barbie doll and her pool! It's easy to fill and empty for an instant pool party. Help Barbie climb the ladder and go down the slide, then relax in the water with a refreshing drink!

toys.name: Barbie & Stacie Sister Doll Set
toys.description: Barbie and Stacie jump into summer adventures together! Just like in the movie Barbie and Stacie to the Rescue, big sis Barbie wears an off-the-shoulder dress with a ruffle collar.

toys.name: Pop Up Super Mario Game
toys.description: In Classic play, Mario is in his pipe and you have to help him get out. Each player takes turns sliding paddles into the pipe. When the correct slot is picked…POP! Mario will bounce out of the pipe and that player wins the game.

toys.name: Gabby's Dollhouse Press-O-Matic
toys.description: Gabby's Dollhouse Press-O-Matic game is an exciting family game where players try to reach the finish line before their opponents, land on an opponent's piece to send them back to the starting line!

toys.name: Hedbanz Light Speed
toys.description: From Spin Master Games, Hedbanz is fun for the whole family. Play your favorite quick question game at lightspeed! Rules change in a flash as your electronic headband lights up one of three colors. Guess as many cards as you can before your headband sings, signaling your time has run out!

toys.name: Bunny Mixer 14 Pieces Set
toys.description: Get ready for a hopping good time with our Bunny Mixer! This cute bunny holds the mixer in its front paws, making baking a magical adventure. The set includes everything your child needs to whip up imaginary delicious treats, from cookies to cupcakes

toys.name: Qwirkle Board Game
toys.description: Players score points by building rows and columns of brightly-coloured tiles that are either all the same colour or all the same shape, without creating duplicates; create a line of all six in a row, and you score a Qwirkle.

toys.name: My Fuzzy Friends Lumies Interactive Virtual Pet - Assorted*
toys.description: Meet the magical Lumies! With a simple tap, Lumies can glow ANY color and even turn colors into musical beats! Match Lumies to your outfit, play 3 interactive games, and discover a rainbow-charged world!

toys.name: Minecraft Make Your Own Alex
toys.description: Make Your Own Minecraft Alex from sustainable materials! Once the easy to assemble cardboard kits are complete, you can pose Alex and add accessories like pickaxes and helmets!

toys.name: Monster Jam 1:64 Die Cast Truck - Assorted*
toys.description: Introducing the all-new, official 1:64 scale die-cast Monster Jam monster truck! This lean, mean, Monster Jam machine features awesome graphics and details. With official BKT Tires, stylized rims, and an authentic chassis, this monster truck embodies the style and swagger of its real-life counterpart!

toys.name: Hot Wheels Multi-Loop Raceoff
toys.description: For exciting racing that's downright loopy, the Hot Wheels Multi-Loop Race Off Playset delivers! Race down the track through a series of loops to score points and be the first through the massive loop, busting it open and leaving the competition in the dust.

toys.name: Battleship Splash Game
toys.description: This ultra-collectible, ultra-squeezable Disney plush is made with soft, high-quality materials. Add this detailed and classic Mickey Mouse plush with his adorable ears to your Squishmallow Squad.

toys.name: Happy Kid Space Blaster
toys.description: Be battle-prepared with the Space Blaster from Happy Kid. Featuring a light up blade, laser booster, ergonomic handle and the option to convert between pistol and sword mode, this Space Blaster is a must-have in your arsenal!

toys.name: Rusco Racing 1:10 Dirt Maxx Motorbike
toys.description: 1:10 Scale so super large motorbike and full suspension system for easy riding

toys.name: Grafix Dinosaur Operation Game
toys.description: Keep your hands steady to avoid having a shocker in the Dinosaur Operation Game.Grab the most body parts and get the most points to win! A great game for 2-4 players. Please note: 2 x AA batteries are required (not included).

toys.name: One Trick Pony
toys.description: Howdy partner! This cowboy is keepin' a watchful eye over his farm and isn't afraid to hogtie any varmint who tries to mess with his herd. His lasso is fast, so step lively! Take turns trying to sneak his animals across the fence - but don't get caught!

toys.name: Gabby's Dollhouse Monopoly Jr
toys.description: Visit Gabby's Dollhouse in this a-meow-zing edition of MONOPOLY Junior! Jump around the game board visiting the Gabby Cats and exploring their rooms, from Cakey's Kitchen to DJ's Music Room. Land on CatRat, Kitty Fairy and Pandy Paws!

toys.name: Nerf Minecraft Heartstealer Dart Blaster
toys.description: These huggable 8 and 12 PAW Patrol plush feature everyone's favorite rescue dogs in their classic uniforms with adorable minimalist designs and accurate details from the cartoon.

toys.name: Sonic Prime Action Figures 6 Pack Deluxe Box - Assorted*
toys.description: Collect all 8 officially licensed Sonic Prime figures, based off your favourite characters from the record breaking Netflix show. Each Deluxe Box contains 6 x 7.5cm figures, each sitting on a black play or display base. Collect Sonic, Tails, Amy Rose, Doctor Eggman, and more!

toys.name: Littlest Pet Shop Farm Besties Collector 5 Pack
toys.description: Calling all new and original Littlest Pet Shop fans! LPS Generation 7 has arrived. Collect a new generation of bobblin' head pets with over 65 exciting new friends in series 1. Panda, cat, axolotl, anteater and so many more are eager to become your new besties!

toys.name: Pokemon TCG: Scarlet & Violet - Temporal Forces Blister Pack - Assorted*
toys.description: The ranks of Ancient and Future Pokémon continue to grow! Walking Wake ex breaks free of the past alongside Raging Bolt ex, while Iron Leaves ex delivers high-tech justice with Iron Crown ex

toys.name: Hard Quiz Fast Game
toys.description: Play Hard Quiz - Hard and Fast! Just like the popular TV Quiz Show you can play an Expert Round, Tom's Round and People's Round. Are you buzzing for bees? Or passionate for punk rock? Find out could win Hard Quiz, at home. Age 13+

toys.name: Monkey Around
toys.description: The Wiggle & Giggle Game prompting players to do simple movements such as balancing, hopping and marching together. Parent guide included. Kids learn hand-eye coordination, imitation, and gross motor-skills while building their vocabulary!
